, her mother beat her. BEAT HER! She was twenty-five. That story is the basis of my sexual education and has reiterated why it\'s important to wait until you\'re married to give it up. So now, every time I go out with a guy, my mom says, &quot;Ojos abiertos, piernas cerradas.&quot; Eyes open, legs closed. That\'s as far as the birds and the bees talk has gone. And I don\'t mind it. I don\'t necessarily agree with that whole wait until you\'re married crap, though. I mean, this is America and the 21st century; not Mexico one hundred years ago. But, of course, I can\'t tell my mom that because she will think I\'m bad. Or worse: trying to be White.\n\n Gabi is Isabel Quintero\'s debut novel.\n\nNamed to Kirkus Reviews Best Books of 2014\n\nNamed to School Library Journal Best Books of 2014<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"15035007510866756142\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'16_book_20702546\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"pWN4eBSqDUwMBP5VDnTguuCwZhJLbZaAU3/rVwDX/HRRvC2Vit1YJHHesMKKKG2n4cfvFMz5PJHyqs8qRL3f1A==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"20702546\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"16_book_20702546\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"ref\" id=\"ref\" value=\"\" class=\"wtrLeftUpRef\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"existing_review\" id=\"existing_review\" value=\"false